MOTION DOCKET

95-595. State ex rel. Capitol Materials Co. v. Trimble.

Franklin App. No. 94APD02-138. On motion to advance case on docket. Motion denied.

Lundberg Stratton, J., also notes that the motion is moot. Douglas, Resnick and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., dissent and would grant the motion.
